Thank you for downloading
cs_nakatomi (v1.0)
by Christmas Turkey

Description:

cs_nakatomi is a Die Hard map for the very popular, Counterstrike:Source. It is based on the first Die Hard movie, starring Bruce Willis. The map itself is a hostage rescue map, consisting of three levels; rooftop (CT spawn), office/contsruction floor and the nakatomi skylobby (T spawn)

Features:

- A variety of ways to navigate the map (ventilation system, elevator shaft, stairwell etc.)
- 16 player support
- An amazing die hard experience
